item.title: Need help with changing magics from reg to ancient
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

setSidebarInterface(6, 12855);

Edit:

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("magic") && playerRights >= 2) if (playerAncientMagics == true) { setSidebarInterface(6, 1151); playerAncientMagics = false; } else { setSidebarInterface(6, 12855); playerAncientMagics = true; }
Have fun. :o
